	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>url bbcode doesn't accept double quotes</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />the param in a bbcode goes between the open and close of a tag
<br />
<br />the option portion is after the = sign in the tail end of the opening tag
<br />
<br />the option for the url bbcode does not accept double quotes in it's regex.
<br />
<br />you need to use Easy Mod then apply Custom BBCode Mod in order to easily correct this.
<br />
<br />the glitch fix is automatically included in the Custom BBCode Mod if i recall correctly.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


